OL,3,CRotherham residents frustrated over
OL,4,Chalt to paid brown bin service
OL,6,FGarden waste collections in Rotherham
OL,7,Fhave been suspended with immediate
OL,8,Feffect until the end of August, amid a
OL,9,Fstaff shortage.
OL,11,FThe decision, announced by Rotherham
OL,12,FCouncil, means households will not
OL,13,Freceive their usual brown bin
OL,14,Fcollection service for the rest of the
OL,15,Fmonth.
OL,17,FGarden waste collections in the town
OL,18,Fare paid for with a subscription
OL,19,Fservice, with residents paying out an
OL,20,Fannual fee of more than #40 to sign up.
