OL,4,Chalt to paid brown bin service
OL,6,FNorman Anderson, a resident in
OL,7,FTodwick, is concerned about the pause
OL,8,Fto bin collections, as his garden
OL,9,Fmaintenance results in lots of waste.
OL,11,F"The question of course is 'Where do
OL,12,Fwe put the stuff? How do we get rid of
OL,13,Fit?"
OL,15,F"My trees are starting to get ready
OL,16,Ffor cutting, got the secateurs ready
OL,17,Fand I have nowhere to put the stuff.
OL,18,FThe bins full."
