OL,3,CRotherham residents frustrated over
OL,4,Chalt to paid brown bin service
OL,6,FNorman is being supported by his local
OL,7,Fcouncillor Cllr Joshua Bacon who says
OL,8,Fhe wasn't given any forewarning about
OL,9,Fthis from the council.
OL,11,F"The bins full."
OL,13,FCllr Bacon, who represents Aston &
OL,14,FTodwick, said: "I have had lots of
OL,15,Fcorrespondence from rightly frustrated
OL,16,Fresidents."
OL,18,FThe council said it was prioritising
OL,19,Fgeneral waste collections to ensure
OL,20,Fessential services continue.
