OL,3,CRotherham residents frustrated over
OL,4,Chalt to paid brown bin service
OL,6,FIn a statement, the authority said:
OL,7,F"We understand this is frustrating and
OL,8,Fsincerely apologise for the
OL,9,Finconvenience.
OL,11,F"Please be assured that we are
OL,12,Factively recruiting new staff to
OL,13,Fbolster the service and making changes
OL,14,Fintended to make it more efficient and
OL,15,Feffective in the future."
OL,17,FAndrew Bramidge, Strategic Director
OL,18,FRegeneration and Environment at
OL,19,FRotherham Council said: "We have got
OL,20,Fpeople starting this week and next
OL,21,Fweek."
