OL,3,CRotherham residents frustrated over
OL,4,Chalt to paid brown bin service
OL,6,F"Normally we recruit agency staff to
OL,7,Fbackfill but this year for some reason
OL,8,Fthere's been less agency staff around."
OL,10,FHe added: "We are very sorry we've had
OL,11,Fto take this action but we have had to
OL,12,Fprioritise so that we can focus on the
OL,13,Ftypes of waste that are more
OL,14,Fproblematic at this time of year."
OL,16,FResidents who have already placed
OL,17,Ftheir brown bins out for collection
OL,18,Fhave been asked to return them from
OL,19,Fthe kerbside.
