OL,3,CRotherham residents frustrated over
OL,4,Chalt to paid brown bin service
OL,6,FGarden waste collections are expected
OL,7,Fto resume on Monday 1 September.
OL,9,FThe council said it would issue
OL,10,Fanother update by Friday 29 August if
OL,11,Ffurther delays occur.
OL,13,FThe authority said it was "considering
OL,14,Fthe best way to make amends" to
OL,15,Fsubscribers for the disruption and
OL,16,Fwould share further information in due
OL,17,Fcourse.
